OL,3,CMaternity review chair resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FThe woman conducting a review into
OL,7,Fmaternity and neonatal services at a
OL,8,FWelsh health board has stood down with
OL,9,Fimmediate effect.
OL,11,FMargaret Bowron KC had been appointed
OL,12,Fby Swansea Bay University Health Board
OL,13,F(SBUHB) to oversee the independent
OL,14,Freview.
OL,16,FWriting to the health board, she said
OL,17,Fit is her belief that her presence had
OL,18,Fbecome an unwelcome distraction from
OL,19,Fthe work of the review.
