OL,6,FCriticism had been levelled at the
OL,7,Fchair by some of the families who
OL,8,Fcampaigned for the review.
OL,10,FIn her resignation letter, Ms Bowron
OL,11,Fsaid: "I accepted the role of Chair
OL,12,Fwith a genuine desire to play my role
OL,13,Fin the Review, which would operate
OL,14,Fentirely independently of the Health
OL,15,FBoard, focussed on seeking to restore
OL,16,Fpatient confidence in local services
OL,17,Fat a time when this has sadly been
OL,18,Feroded.
