OL,6,F"That loss of confidence is also
OL,7,Fhaving a detrimental impact on staff
OL,8,Fwhen, in keeping with the rest of the
OL,9,FUK, the service is under immense and
OL,10,Fsustained pressure.
OL,12,F"Very sadly, over the weeks that have
OL,13,Ffollowed, I have come to realise that
OL,14,Fmy appointment has become a
OL,15,Fconsiderable and regrettable
OL,16,Fdistraction to the very aim, which
OL,17,Fmotivated me in accepting the role of
OL,18,FChair, being achieved.
