OL,6,F"I have very reluctantly concluded
OL,7,Fthat the reins need to be taken up as
OL,8,Fsoon as practicable by another person
OL,9,Fwho can take forward the role without
OL,10,Fsuch distractions."
OL,12,FIn December, Eluned Morgan announced
OL,13,Fthe Welsh Government would conduct
OL,14,Fenhanced monitoring of maternity
OL,15,Fservices over concerns for the care
OL,16,Fgiven to mothers and babies at
OL,17,FSingleton Hospital in Swansea.
