OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales in December, the
OL,7,Ffamily of Gethin Channon, who was born
OL,8,Fwith severe brain damage after
OL,9,Fcomplications during his birth in
OL,10,F2019, welcomed the health minister's
OL,11,Fannouncement of enhanced monitoring of
OL,12,Fthe maternity service but said it
OL,13,Fshould have come sooner.
OL,15,FSBUHB's review into Gethin's birth was
OL,16,Fthen heavily criticised by one of the
OL,17,FUK's top medical investigators Dr Bill
OL,18,FKirkup with accusations the health
OL,19,Fboard covered up the expert's report,
OL,20,Fwhich the service denied.
