OL,10,FRobert Channon, Gethin's father, had
OL,11,Fbeen calling for an independent review
OL,12,Finto the maternity unit in Swansea
OL,13,Falong with opposition politicians in
OL,14,FCardiff Bay
OL,16,F"We are pleased that the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment has finally acknowledged
OL,18,Fthat SBUHB maternity service requires
OL,19,Fgreater review," he told ITV Wales
OL,20,Flast year.
