OL,6,F"However, this is a small step, and
OL,7,Ftoo late for all of the families
OL,8,Faffected in the last 10 years by the
OL,9,Fpoor leadership, clinical care and
OL,10,Fcover-ups taking place at the health
OL,11,Fboard."
OL,13,FMs Bowron has been replaced on an
OL,14,Finterim basis by Dr Denise Chaffer, a
OL,15,Fmidwife and existing member of the
OL,16,Fpanel overseeing the review.
