OL,6,FCommenting, Jan Williams, Chair of
OL,7,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,8,Fsaid: "We would like to place on
OL,9,Frecord our thanks to Mrs Bowron for
OL,10,Fthe work she did in establishing the
OL,11,FOversight Panel and finalising the
OL,12,FTerms of Reference following a
OL,13,Flistening period involving input from
OL,14,Fservice users and staff.
OL,16,F"The Review itself, undertaken by an
OL,17,Fentirely separate review team, is
OL,18,Falready underway and its work will
OL,19,Fgather pace over the coming weeks.
