OL,6,F"In the meantime, the Oversight Panel
OL,7,Fwill be chaired on an interim basis by
OL,8,Fexisting member Dr Denise Chaffer, an
OL,9,Fexperienced leader in maternity and
OL,10,Fpatient safety.
OL,12,F"Dr Chaffer has no previous
OL,13,Finvolvement with our Health Board
OL,14,Fbefore being independently appointed
OL,15,Fto the Oversight Panel. I would like
OL,16,Fto thank Dr Chaffer for agreeing to
OL,17,Ftake up the role on an interim basis."
