OL,6,FResponding, Dr Chaffer said: "This
OL,7,Freview was set up to address the
OL,8,Fconcerns raised about maternity and
OL,9,Fneonatal services. Taking on the role
OL,10,Fof Chair today, gives the opportunity
OL,11,Fto take this important Review further
OL,12,Fforward. Hearing the voice of parents
OL,13,Fand wider stakeholders will be central
OL,14,Fto my approach, to ensure we can
OL,15,Fdeliver meaningful change together.
OL,17,F"Next steps will be meeting with a
OL,18,Frange of maternity and neonatal
OL,19,Fservice users to hear and discuss
OL,20,Ftheir views about this Review going
OL,21,Fforward."
